{"tid":192621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"周身都損 點去疤","createTime":"2017-04-08T16:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T15:41:14.000Z","uid":5821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0309310e1a88bfe0cb0b21e31b99e15ac9feb1","tid":192621,"uid":5821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:55:09.000Z","msg":"唉由細到大都會成日周身損 <br />\n又成日生暗瘡 又會r損 忍唔到手<br />\n成日就結完焦 留低咗黑色點點係身到好煩<br />\n基本上可以講係全身無一個完整無缺皮光肉滑既地方<br />\n好煩惱 又夏天 <br />\n今日數過兩隻腳加埋有成100粒損咗既地方<br />\n真係好肉酸點算好<br />\n夏天露到少少隻腳出黎比人見到爛到隻腳好似中毒咁<br />\n好醜好柒啊 有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc7e5a060ee5add238a073151a30e8bec27deb6","tid":192621,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我背脊都係 有咩方法"},{"pid":"3315dc8f1717c7935da0cd49ef5365b76736f329","tid":192621,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"唔可以留手指甲<br />\n護膚品唔理係toner 定lotion定cream照搽落去(只係印唔係叫你搽傷口)<br />\n沖涼用磨沙去死皮產品<br />\n用美白功能既body cream"},{"pid":"eeff113cfbe4c11dfc96aafd54ff67721caca0f2","tid":192621,"uid":5821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我背脊都係 有咩方法</blockquote><br />\n屌 我都係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去日本買咗支野 止佢生粒粒<br />\n生少咗 但花到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0bacbaf6553269bcd7cf9adef8c06a6c618d21","tid":192621,"uid":5821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以留手指甲<br />\n護膚品唔理係toner 定lotion定cream照搽落去(只係印唔係叫你搽傷口)<br />\n沖涼用磨沙去死皮產品<br />\n用美白功能既body cream</blockquote><br />\n 去死皮同美白有咩好推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f553a5ac7e65725f6dff215cd27926854209de14","tid":192621,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"100粒真係數出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d689d894aac18c51d6e7546034ae444e94be7c2","tid":192621,"uid":5821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>100粒真係數出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒得濟望住自己對腳 太嘔心"},{"pid":"7e593b09bc4bf53cd77d4498f638cfcd6cf411ac","tid":192621,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我背脊都係 有咩方法</blockquote><br />\n屌 我都係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前去日本買咗支野 止佢生粒粒<br />\n生少咗 但花到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己睇唔到 就成日用手整佢 叫家姐幫我我茶啲暗倉膏 佢話好多 好似滿天星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398c88430b0ee0d0732d12f7a07bb33bc05716e3","tid":192621,"uid":46863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"same here<br />\n一樣係小腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過夏天照著短褲<br />\n啲fd 親戚會好似發現新大陸咁問隻腳咩事"},{"pid":"93f4f2cadbe822e8b41f5711adc71f3666920453","tid":192621,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"我有一排R到個背隻花曬 照鏡見到都想死<br />\n其實我都唔知點解痕同埋訓教都識R,總之就唔好留指甲先<br />\n果陣買左隻黑色既日本沖涼皂用完就慢慢好左<br />\n<br />\n之後到去印 果排因為專注想去印所以都花左少少錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Z0c7C6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Z0c7C6.jpg&h=df5e5fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食之美白針,一日一包或者兩包隨你喜歡. 加上幾好味<br />\n我好似用左兩三個月就停左,好有幫助,唔化妝都比同事問搽左乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以去印都去左好多<br />\n但如果唔想下下$5xx咁買就可以skip<br />\n<br />\n沖涼我用有磨砂粒粒既野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMt1j80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMt1j80.jpg&h=14fe6ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近排用緊呢隻,可以日日用同埋唔會好粗粒粒唔會洗痛洗損<br />\n其實好多日本出既美白皂都可以全身用<br />\n我就乜都用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沖完涼搽既野都好多選擇<br />\n以下係我覺得有用既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/09/012203_8c5a9e900474dc6e2a56af3f3f09a065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2F012203_8c5a9e900474dc6e2a56af3f3f09a065.jpg&h=7438c741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/09/012229_b7e444cf52cfb85f92accf3c2f25d9aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2F012229_b7e444cf52cfb85f92accf3c2f25d9aa.jpg&h=0ab09044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tXV0rE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tXV0rE.jpg&h=f9827809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求其既話其實搽skincare果陣pat埋落去係咁咦捽下都算做左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ff93bad87d649b4b3be9b83ff9df8e69eb7df1","tid":192621,"uid":5821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有一排R到個背隻花曬 照鏡見到都想死<br />\n其實我都唔知點解痕同埋訓教都識R,總之就唔好留指甲先<br />\n果陣買左隻黑色既日本沖涼皂用完就慢慢好左<br />\n<br />\n之後到去印 果排因為專注想去印所以都花左少少錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Z0c7C6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Z0c7C6.jpg&h=df5e5fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><b